high_descs: Turn around and walk around the kitchen island to the counter left of the stove.
Pick up the sponge on the counter.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Wash the sponge in the sink.
Turn around and walk to the end of the counter, to the shelves.
Place the sponge on the shelf, to the right of the book.
